{"tid":371041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（睇人仆街最開心）大澳小店全毀：請不要慶祝風假","createTime":"2017-08-23T11:41:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T07:25:17.000Z","uid":29314,"like":8,"dislike":152,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4547531db4bf7861a79d4deec2c1aa33d70c0b5e","tid":371041,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:41:23.000Z","msg":"風暴期間大澳市內多處出現嚴重水浸，洪水一度湧入吉慶街和永安大街，水深及腰。&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n在吉慶街街上開設環保服裝店的本地品牌「EARTH.er」全店慘被洪水淹沒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n負責人中午在店舖facebook專頁中留言「請不要慶祝風球，你換來的是假期，別人換來的是痛苦」&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「成間舖冇晒，浸到上腰」，慨嘆「小店經歷過對面棚屋大火、多次風災，但今次終於都避唔過」，又指全店貨物應該已經全毀！"},{"pid":"064d48d7123574dcf7573cbbb43b3ae06131ed5a","tid":371041,"uid":29314,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170823/large/1503476070_0d2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170823%2Flarge%2F1503476070_0d2a.jpg&h=9e5295de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17daa1954fa4bb4e9726062e0679eb1c901858bd","tid":371041,"uid":33878,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:42:54.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"c289bc89501ca8b182b3968da9d312839852494c","tid":371041,"uid":23170,"like":302,"dislike":3,"score":299,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:43:38.000Z","msg":"因為一個人唔開心，全世界都要唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ea0ac0111756131c1b42162b85fe97b7bb152c","tid":371041,"uid":491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:44:11.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9529a9562ed979ba8400166778d0bf475c75e7","tid":371041,"uid":33572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/